{"word":"G255 - ἀλυσιτελής - alysitelḗs - al-oo-sit-el-ace' - Unprofitable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀλυσιτελής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">alysitelḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">al-oo-sit-el-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unprofitable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரயோசனமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unprofitable, hurtful, pernicious"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and the base of <a href=\"#/G3081 - λυσιτελεῖ - lysiteleî - loo-sit-el-i'/3081\">G3081</a>; <i>gainless</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>pernicious:</i> - unprofitable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}